%^BOLD%^-=%^BLUE%^Water Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

The water domain pulls solely from the power of elemental
water.  Like water, some of its effects are healing, while
others can be destructive.

Clerics with the Water Domain gain the following benefits:
- Permanent water breathing.
- %^BOLD%^BLUE%^Ice Bolt%^RESET%^ as an innate spell.

The water domain contains the following spells:

Sleet Storm, Solid Fog, Cone of Cold, Vortex, Seamantle

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Lysara, Seija

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
